name: estatesalesforla
overview:
Estate Sales for L.A. is a full service estate sales company in Los Angeles and serving clients of Southern California since 1988. Whatever your needs are like consolidation of your home, relocation, Estate Sales for L.A. handles your estate with care. Contact Estate Sales For L.A. for a free consultation and appraisal today!

Our services include:

  1. Professional and effective estate sales conducted in your home if needed.
  2. We can help you to purchase of entire estate or single items
  3. Consignment
  4. Free expert consultations and evaluations to determine what best fits your needs

Contact Details: Estate Sales for L.A. 3103 W. 6th Street Los Angeles, CA 90020
Telephone: (213) 999-7773 Email: info@estatesalesforla.com http://www.estatesalesforla.com/
